  "texts": [
    "For instance, LLMs can be used to generate imaginative and creative content, such as fiction, poetry, or art descriptions, pushing the boundaries of traditional human creativity [44][45][46].",
    "This kind of creativity is required for generating new and unique cybersecuirty exercises scenarios and LLMs hallucination can play an important role in it.",
    "Scenario Design ProcessTaking inspiration from eLuna [47] game design process we theorized to use the same approach to create scenarios for cybersecurity exercises.",
    "The eLuna framework exemplifies a methodical brainstorming process tailored for the collaborative design of narrative Digital Game-Based Learning (DGBL) experiences.",
    "It facilitates a creative dialogue between educators and game developers, employing a visual language to articulate and merge educational objectives with engaging gameplay elements."
  ]
